<plot>Louis, who runs a family operated restaurant in the outskirts of a small village, is well-known to have a gift in resurrecting the dead. However, he does not accept these acknowledgements concerning himself. One night, he is visited by a bride and a groom, due to the sudden death of the bride's father before the wedding. According to their customs, marriage can not take place within six months in the presence of a death. However, the bride is pregnant and the wedding must proceed regardless. Does Louis actually have the power to revive the dead and help the couple in time?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?250268</url></doc>
